cmprovision4 (1.6.4+nureva.1) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Implement optional MAC address allocation
  * Add script to set assigned MAC address in config.txt (via migrations)
  * Implement query strings for sorting and limiting cms APi routes
  * Add beta route to be able to get latest provision results for each
    provisioning board.
  * Implement re-use of assigned MAC addresses when same device (by serial) is
    re-provisioned.
  * Provide non-colon version of MAC address to printer label

 -- Kiley Hykawy <kiley.hykawy@gmail.com>  Sun, 16 Jul 2023 17:31:45 -0600

cmprovision4 (1.6.4) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add support for detecting which network port devices are connected
    to when using a managed Ethernet switch supporting SNMP BRIDGE-MIB.
    For now: to setup run:
      sudo /var/lib/cmprovision/artisan ethernetswitch:configure

